1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Vicki Monroe conducts an investigation into the violent murder of Wichita, Kansas mother, Vikky Overstreet. Vikky's spirit makes an appearance, providing answers to the questions her family has long been waiting for.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Spirit messenger Vicki Monroe travels to San Antonio, Texas to investigate the 21 year disappearance of army reservist Johnny Perez. Jack King is a prime suspect. If King won't talk Vicki knows his spirits will and hopefully, they'll know Johnny is.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Vicki Monroe visits Toledo, Ohio to investigate the disappearance and murder of Brenda Borowski. When Vicki shares her findings with Brenda's family, she's met with an emotional response - their dreams held the clues all along.

imdb.plot outline: Death row psychic Vicki Monroe investigates the violent murders of Vikky Overstreet, Johnny Perez, and Brenda Borowski. If the convicts of these murders on death row won't talk, she knows the spirits of their victims will. Will the families of these victims finally get the answers they have been waiting for?
